Source: wb-docker
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Wiren Board Team <info@wirenboard.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/wirenboard/wb-docker

Package: wb-docker
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ca-certificates,
         docker-compose,
         docker.io,
         systemd,
         wb-configs
Description: Wiren Board integration package for Docker
 This package provides Wiren Board specific lifecycle hooks, default
 configuration templates, and recovery contracts around a Debian-packaged
 Docker installation. It depends on Debian Docker packages, but intentionally
 does not ship Docker Engine binaries itself.
